==Finnish==
===Etymology===
Compound of ''mustalais-'' from ''[[mustalainen]]'' and ''[[kieli]]''
===Noun===
'''mustalaiskieli'''

#(''common'') [[Romany]] (the language)

===Synonyms===
*[[romanikieli]]
*[[romani]]

===Usage notes===
This term is widely accepted within the [[roma]] community of Finland. However, it is official and better accepted to use the word [[romanikieli]] or [[romani]].

